us rep larkin smith a former 
sheriff known for his strong lawandorder stance was found dead 
monday with his pilot in the wreckage of a small plane that crashed 
in a forest 
the freshman republican whose plane disappeared sunday evening 
during a 90mile flight from hattiesburg to gulfport became the 
