needle and hooked the patient to a cardiac monitor the 007 
airplane was summoned to take the guard to a hospital in rabat 
morocco 
mission accomplished dorta left the hospital but was stopped 
by soldiers demanding his passport 
i told them its back in the desert on the movie set 
dorta said they put me in a room where i sat and drank tea for 
six hours until the king gave permission for me to leave 
dortas patient recovered after surgery 
if it werent for jimmy i dont think he would have lived 
said michael g wilson who produced and wrote the bond flick 
its that kind of response that is very important to us so when 
it came time to film our next movie we wanted him back 
