whisper to a scream virgin vision vhsbeta 7995 rated r 
 
whisper to a scream is an ordinary movie about serial 
murders in this case the victims are nightclub dancers who get 
sliced and diced by the sleazy joints weirdo disc jockey 
its a an amateurish production at best and one wonders why such 
a distinguished actor as yaphet kotto would want to be in it he 
plays the police detective assigned to solve the murders 
the dancers are supposedly artist types but they do tend to take 
