starting with their very first single the ballad renacer 
they spent the next decade as the worlds only arenawedding band 
wed go to latin america and play huge stadiums 50000 people 
and then wed go back to miami and play a wedding maybe 300 
people estefan said 
we were on latin radio and little by little maybe because 
they could identify with the way i worded things we became more 
popular parents started saying their kids were listening to our 
music even though they hated latin music 
pop success started in early 1986 with the top 10 single 
conga and hasnt let up perserverance she says is the secret 
also the songs like the ballad dont wanna lose you off cuts 
both ways 
we played the song for the cousin of someone in the band she 
was a high school student coming up for a school paper she came in 
